statements: SELECT * FROM lead_sources;
SELECT lead_id, source_name, conversion_rate FROM lead_sources;
SELECT source_name, channel_type FROM lead_sources WHERE lead_quality='High';
SELECT * FROM lead_sources ORDER BY source_name DESC;
SELECT lead_id, channel_type FROM lead_sources WHERE conversion_rate > 0.50;
SELECT * FROM lead_sources WHERE channel_type = 'Social Media' AND lead_quality = 'High' ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT source_name, channel_type FROM lead_sources WHERE conversion_rate > 0.5;
SELECT lead_id, source_name, channel_type, lead_quality, conversion_rate FROM lead_sources WHERE lead_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT * FROM lead_sources WHERE channel_type != 'Email' ORDER BY lead_quality, conversion_rate;
SELECT source_name, channel_type FROM lead_sources WHERE conversion_rate BETWEEN 0.3 AND 0.7 ORDER BY channel_type;
SELECT * FROM lead_sources;
SELECT lead_source_id, lead_source_name, lead_channel_type FROM lead_sources ORDER BY lead_source_name;
SELECT * FROM lead_analysis WHERE lead_count > 10 ORDER BY lead_count DESC;
SELECT lead_source_id, lead_source_name, lead_conversion_rate FROM lead_sources WHERE lead_channel_type = 'Social Media';
SELECT lead_source_id, lead_channel_type, COUNT(lead_source_id) AS lead_count FROM lead_analysis GROUP BY lead_source_id ORDER BY lead_count DESC;
SELECT lead_source_name, lead_channel_type FROM lead_sources;
SELECT lead_source_name, lead_conversion_rate FROM lead_sources ORDER BY lead_conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT lead_source_name, lead_channel_type, lead_conversion_rate FROM lead_sources WHERE lead_conversion_rate > 0.5;
SELECT * FROM lead_sources INNER JOIN lead_analysis ON lead_sources.lead_source_id = lead_analysis.lead_source_id;
SELECT lead_source_name, AVG(lead_conversion_rate) AS avg_conversion_rate FROM lead_analysis GROUP BY lead_source_name ORDER BY avg_conversion_rate DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_sources;
SELECT source_name, channel FROM lead_sources;
SELECT lead_id, lead_date, lead_status FROM lead_generation WHERE lead_status = 'Qualified';
SELECT source_name, channel FROM lead_sources WHERE source_id IN (1, 3, 5);
SELECT channel_name, channel_type FROM marketing_channels WHERE channel_type = 'Digital';
SELECT * FROM lead_generation;
SELECT lead_id, lead_date, lead_status FROM lead_generation WHERE lead_status = 'Qualified';

SELECT l.lead_id, l.lead_date, ls.source_name, lc.channel_name FROM lead_generation l JOIN lead_sources ls ON l.source_id = ls.source_id JOIN marketing_channels lc ON ls.channel = lc.channel_name WHERE l.lead_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-12-31';
SELECT ls.source_name, COUNT(l.lead_id) AS total_leads FROM lead_generation l JOIN lead_sources ls ON l.source_id = ls.source_id GROUP BY ls.source_name ORDER BY total_leads DESC;

SELECT l.lead_id, l.lead_value, lc.channel_type FROM lead_generation l JOIN lead_sources ls ON l.source_id = ls.source_id JOIN marketing_channels lc ON ls.channel = lc.channel_name WHERE l.lead_date < '2022-06-01';
SELECT * FROM LeadSources;
SELECT id, source_name, cost FROM LeadSources WHERE cost > 100;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email FROM Leads ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT * FROM MarketingChannels WHERE channel_type = 'Online';
SELECT lead_name, phone_number FROM Leads WHERE lead_source_id = 2;
SELECT id, source_name, campaign_name, cost, created_at FROM LeadSources WHERE cost > 1000 ORDER BY created_at DESC;
SELECT channel_name, channel_type, description, created_at FROM MarketingChannels WHERE channel_type = 'Social Media' ORDER BY channel_name ASC;
SELECT lead_name, lead_email, phone_number, created_at FROM Leads WHERE lead_email LIKE '%gmail.com' ORDER BY created_at DESC LIMIT 10;
SELECT id, lead_id, conversion_rate, conversion_status, created_at FROM LeadAnalytics WHERE conversion_status = true ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;

SELECT ls.source_name, lc.channel_name, la.conversion_rate, la.created_at FROM LeadSources ls JOIN Leads l ON ls.id = l.lead_source_id JOIN MarketingChannels lc ON l.lead_source_id = lc.id JOIN LeadAnalytics la ON l.id = la.lead_id ORDER BY la.created_at DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_sources;
SELECT source_name, channel FROM lead_sources WHERE lead_id = 1;
SELECT DISTINCT source_type FROM lead_sources ORDER BY source_type ASC;
SELECT channel_name, channel_description FROM marketing_channels WHERE channel_type = 'Paid Social';
SELECT campaign_id, start_date, end_date, total_leads_generated FROM campaign_performance ORDER BY total_leads_generated DESC;
SELECT * FROM lead_sources WHERE source_type = 'Organic';
SELECT lead_id, channel FROM lead_sources WHERE source_name LIKE 'Google%';
SELECT source_name, channel FROM lead_sources WHERE channel = 'Social Media' ORDER BY source_name ASC;
SELECT channel_name, channel_description FROM marketing_channels WHERE channel_type = 'Paid' ORDER BY channel_name DESC;
SELECT * FROM conversion_rates WHERE date_range = '2021 Q3' AND conversion_rate > 20 ORDER BY conversion_rate DESC;
